videos.description: Jordan Nwora is unfazed by the defense and knocks down a shot from deep for Louisville's first points of the game.
videos.headline: Nwora drains contested triple

videos.description: Louisville opens the game on fire from 3-point range, connecting on their first five shots from downtown.
videos.headline: Louisville starts hot from deep

videos.description: Louisville freshman Samuell Williamson follows up a missed shot by slamming home a powerful putback dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Williamson cleans up with putback slam) 2019/11/13

videos.headline: Williamson cleans up with putback slam

videos.description: Louisville's Aidan Igiehon misses a free throw, but gets the ball back and rises up over a defender for a big slam.
videos.headline: Igiehon elevates for powerful dunk

videos.description: Louisville's Jordan Nwora drives, absorbs contact and adjusts in the air to score the basket, plus the foul.
videos.headline: Nwora banks in tough and-1 bucket
